messages.message: Hi @CJ. It happens with any of the fields. I can't see a "Save Fields" button, so it's not possible to save any changes. The strange thing is that it happens with more than one browser: Thorium, Chrome, and Firefox. Do those browser use some kind of external library that may be causing the problem? Java, perhaps?
Check your setting for your user.  Make sure to have auto save features turned off
